HEADWORD: Foreshot
<hw>Fore"shot`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>In distillation of
low wines, the first portion of spirit that comes over, being a fluid
abounding in fusel oil.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

